<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261336>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Holotype of Sitana marudhamneydhal sp. nov. (NCBS AQ 460) from Kallidaikurichi, Tamil Nadu. (A) full body dorsal (B) flank region (C) dorsal view of head (D) lateral view of head. Scale bar: 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261337>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Sitana marudhamneydhal sp. nov. A. An adult male from the type locality Kallidaikurichi. B. An adult female from the type locality (Uncollected specimens)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261337/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261338>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Hemipenis of Sitana marudhamneydhal sp. nov. CES 141196, 53.8 mm SVL. (A) asulcal view; (B) sulcal view. Scale bar: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.261339>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Habitat of Sitana marudhamneydhal sp. nov. A. type locality Mayiladumparai in Kallidaikurichi, B. Sunset Point, near Kanyakumari." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/261339/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

